title.@value: Fetus or newborn affected by maternal injury

definition.@value: A group of conditions characterised by findings in the fetus or newborn due to conditions in the mother resulting from physical damage or harm.

label.@value: Fetus or newborn affected by maternal injury, poisoning or certain other consequences of external causes
